Sprint Planning Meeting
	What?- The sprint goal gives direction to the team. Analysis, evaluation, and selection from Product Backlog defines Sprint backlog 


How?- Create an actionable plan for delivery. Ensure the right amount of work is tackled.
	Estimation
	The act of determining (guessing) the expected size of something.
In scrum, estimating helps to set expectations as to the amount of work that can be performed or the length of time until something is finished 
	



