Daily Standup
Purpose
Come up with a plan for the next 24 hours to ensure that we move forward toward a successful increment 
	3 Questions


What have you done since the last meeting?


What are you planning to do before the next meeting? 


Do you experience any obstacles?


	Rules


Strictly 15 minutes 
	





Pair Programming 


Two team members working on the same task 
	

